'''Małgorzata Pudlik''' is a [[J.R.R. Tolkien|Tolkien]] artist who has illustrated numerous calendars, including:
* [[The Tolkien Calendar 1991 (Poland)]]
* [[The Tolkien Calendar 1992]]
* [[The Tolkien Calendar 1993 (Polish)]]
* [[The Tolkien Calendar 1994 (Polish)]]
* [[Tolkien Calendar 1995 (Polish)]]
* [[Tolkien Calendar 1996]]
* [[Simbelmyne Calendar 1999 (Polish)]]
